msgstr "La batalla de Arras"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/story"
msgid ""
"The Battle of France is reaching a critical stage. The German thrust through "
"the Ardennes forest has been very successful, as their armored spearhead "
"reaches the Channel coast near Abbeville on this day. \n"
"\n"
"The Allies must counterattack to cut off the German breakthrough, or face "
"certain defeat. \n"
"\n"
"The British will counterattack from Arras today, with almost all of their "
"remaining armor. \n"
"\n"
"After a stop at Vimy you have now reached the starting line. \n"
"\n"
"The fate of France - and that of the entire BEF - depends on this "
"counterattack. You have to stop the Germans at all costs!"
msgstr ""
"La batalla de Francia está llegando a una fase crítica. El avance alemán a "
"través del bosque de las Ardenas ha sido muy exitoso, ya que su punta de "
"lanza blindada ha llegado hoy a la costa del Canal de la Mancha, cerca de "
"Abbeville. \n"
"\n"
"Los aliados deben contraatacar para detener el avance alemán o se "
"enfrentarán a una derrota segura. Los británicos contraatacarán hoy desde "
"Arras con casi todos los blindados que les quedan. Tras una parada en Vimy, "
"has llegado a la línea de salida. El destino de Francia, y el de todo el "
"Cuerpo Expedicionario Británico, depende de este contraataque. ¡Tienes que "
"detener a los alemanes a toda costa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/place"
msgid "British Expeditionary Force"
msgstr "Fuerza Expedicionaria Británica"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/date"
msgid "May 20th, 1940 · Achicourt, France"
msgstr "20 de mayo de 1940 · Achicourt, Francia"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Well done, we have well and truly given the Germans something to think "
"about! This will undoubtedly raise morale among the troops. Even if we "
"didn’t stop the German advance, at least we slowed it down."
msgstr ""
"¡Bien hecho, les hemos dado a los alemanes algo en qué pensar! Sin duda, "
"esto levantará la moral de las tropas. Aunque no hayamos detenido el avance "
"alemán, al menos lo hemos ralentizado."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This counts as a costly failure; because we allowed our attack to be "
"stopped, the Germans can now continue the encirclement of our main force. We "
"must regroup and try again, after reporting to HQ. "
msgstr ""
"Esto se considera un fracaso costoso; al permitir que se detuviera nuestro "
"ataque, los alemanes ahora pueden continuar el cerco de nuestras fuerzas "
"principales. Debemos reagruparnos e intentarlo de nuevo, después de informar "
"al cuartel general. "

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/outro_failed_hq"
msgid ""
"Bloody hell… We failed to secure our field HQ! you need to go back and get "
"another effort going!"
msgstr ""
"Maldita sea... ¡No hemos conseguido asegurar nuestro cuartel general de "
"campaña! ¡Tienes que volver y volver a intentarlo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/mission_hq"
msgid "You must hold your field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Debes mantener tu cuartel general de campo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/mission_attack"
msgid "Punch a hole in the enemy position and drive north!"
msgstr "¡Abre una brecha en la posición enemiga y avanza hacia el norte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 German positions!"
msgstr "¡Tus soldados han asegurado %1%/7 posiciones alemanas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome back to the front line, Lieutenant! This is our field HQ, it must "
"remain in our control!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido de nuevo al frente, teniente! Este es nuestro cuartel general de "
"campaña, ¡debe permanecer bajo nuestro control!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"Counter-attack is in full swing, a swift assault is necessary to breach "
"through the German lines."
msgstr ""
"El contraataque está en pleno apogeo, es necesario un ataque rápido para "
"romper las líneas alemanas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"Be quick, be decisive, and try not to lose too many men! Use the terrain to "
"your advantage."
msgstr ""
"¡Sé rápido, sé decisivo y trata de no perder demasiados hombres! Aprovecha "
"el terreno a tu favor."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/narrator_start3"
msgid ""
"More reinforcements will become available as you progress with your assault!"
msgstr ""
"¡A medida que avances en tu asalto, tendrás más refuerzos a tu disposición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Gentlemen! Germans are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr ""
"¡Señores! ¡Los alemanes están cerca de nuestro cuartel general de campaña!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/allied_survivors_assign"
msgid "Thanks for coming to our aid Lieutenant! We are under your command now."
msgstr ""
"¡Gracias por venir en nuestra ayuda, teniente! Ahora estamos bajo tu mando."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "We must hold our command post! There is no room for surrender!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos mantener nuestro puesto de mando! ¡No hay lugar para la rendición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/narrator_ambush"
msgid ""
"Bloody hell! One of our tanks and trucks got lost and knocked out. We should "
"try and recover this tank!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea! Uno de nuestros tanques y camiones se ha perdido y ha quedado "
"fuera de combate. ¡Deberíamos intentar recuperar este tanque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrike."
msgstr "¡Comandante! Ahora puedes solicitar un ataque aéreo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/tasks/extra"
msgid "Recover Matilda tank!"
msgstr "¡Recupera el tanque Matilda!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/tasks/secret01"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/tasks/secret01_completed"
msgid ""
"Secret objective #1: Retribution - killed 10+ enemy soldiers in a short time."
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto n.º 1: Venganza: matar a más de 10 soldados enemigos en "
"poco tiempo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/tasks/secret02"
msgid "Secret objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 2"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1940_05_20_arras_skirmish/tasks/secret02_completed"
msgid "Secret objective #2: Top Gun - rapidly destroyed 3 enemy vehicles."
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto n.º 2: Top Gun: destruir rápidamente 3 vehículos enemigos."
